Detailed Description

cvmx_nqm_vf::_vec::_msix_addr

NQM_VF(x)_VEC(0..16)_MSIX_ADDR contains the address portion of the PCI-standard MSI-X table for function x. NQM_VF_MODE[VF_MODE] selects the MSI-X table entries that are actually present in the hardware. The NQM_VF_INT_VEC_E enumeration describes the table entries available in each function. See NQM_VF_INT_VEC_E and NQM_VF_MODE_E.

For how to migrate these CSRs, see the NQM_VF()_MSIX_PBA description.
